response.overview: Kerrigan is attracted to a mysterious ancient relic at the depths of a temple. Many have gone before her, but none have returned. Upon her visit, Kerrigan gets caught by the same monster that made everyone else vanish. She is covered in its cocoon and swallowed whole, unable to make a move before she becomes yet another prey of the monster. Kerrigan suddenly wakes...
response.title: Kerrigans Last Trip
